message:
Task finished.

I implemented and tested the solution at /workspace/solution.py (sieve up to floor(sqrt(N)); counts primes p with p^8 ≤ N and distinct prime pairs p<q with p*q ≤ floor(sqrt(N))). I also created /workspace/eval_test.py (brute-force verifier for small N) and /workspace/evaluation.txt (scores and reasoning). I ran the provided samples and exhaustive checks up to N=5000; results matched expected outputs (e.g., N=200 → 3, N=4_000_000_000_000 → 407073). To run the solution: echo 200 | python3 /workspace/solution.py or python3 /workspace/solution.py < input.txt. No further action required.
